item.title: Team onxy client
item.dc:creator: @Dylan123321 Dylan123321
item.description:
@Dylan123321 wrote:

I have the client my self just make sure when they use these commands i will post the commands below make sure that it kicks them (If you know how to do that) another tip is don’t give your skype out i can easily get your ip out of your skype here are the commands below

//Usefull Exploits//

::curse = Switches to Ancient Curses.
::modern = Switches to the default spellbook.
::ancients = Switches to Ancient Magicks.
::lunars = Switches to the Lunar Spellbook.
: = Restores your prayer points.
::b = Opens up your bank.
::wb = Opens up your bank (In wilderness too).
::dep = Deposits your inventory to your bank.
::al = Uses all bones in your inventory on an altar.
::log = Instantly logs out, usefull for duping.

//Fun Exploits//

::web = Spawns a web.
::webs = Spawns 9 webs in a 3x3 area.
::clip = Enables Noclip.
::z = Transforms you into other players.
::cart = Turns you into a cart.

//Dungeoneering Exploits//

::mage = Gets Dungeoneering Mage Class.
::melee = Gets Dungeoneering Melee Class.
::range = Gets Dungeoneering Range Class.

//Teleporting Exploits//

::torms = Teleports you to Donator Only Tormented Demons.
::barrel = Teleports you to Donator Only Barrelchest.
::metaldrags = Teleports you to Donator Only Steel/Iron Dragons.
::hills = Teleports you to Donator Only Hill Giants.
::h = Teleports to Edgeville, usefull for when jailed or in Wilderness.
::gnome = Pulls up the gnome glider interface for teleporting.

//Testing Exploits//

::goup = Goes up in height.
::godown = Goes down in height.
::dataon = Shows coords.
::oi = Opens any interface.
::obj = Clicks on any object.

//Crashing Exploits//
::ddos = Crashes a Server
::bankcrash = Crashed a server
